&lt;p&gt;An exciting opprtunity has a risen for Highly Motivated Band 5 Occupational Therapists to join our staff bank. The purpose of this role is to support the Occupational Therapy services Trustwide as and when this is required.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Essential Criteria:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Diploma or degree in OT&lt;br /&gt;- State registered with HCPC&lt;br /&gt;- Interest or experience in elderly, medical orthopedics surgery and stroke rehab as well as rehabilitation and community work&lt;br /&gt;- Use of evidence based practice&lt;br /&gt;- Application of the O.T. process&lt;br /&gt;- Use of functional assessments and activity analysis&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Advert Closing Date: 10th November 2020&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
